                <h2>A Murrysville Firm Built on Trust</h2>
                <p>Ament Law Group, P.C. is a 12-person law firm in Murrysville, Pennsylvania serving families and businesses across six counties in Western Pennsylvania. Co-founded by W. Robert Ament and John W. Ament, the firm brings over 50 years of combined legal experience to every client relationship.</p>
                <p>Trust is the foundation of every interaction we have with our clients. Our attorneys have successfully represented clients across a wide range of legal matters â€” purchasing homes, establishing and transitioning businesses, drafting estate plans, avoiding probate, and administering estates. This diverse experience enables us to positively impact many aspects of our clients' lives and livelihoods.</p>

                <h2>Our Practice</h2>
                <p>We concentrate our practice in the areas where our experience runs deepest: <a href="/practice-areas/estate-planning/">estate planning</a>, <a href="/practice-areas/probate-administration/">probate and trust administration</a>, <a href="/practice-areas/real-estate-law/">real estate settlement services</a>, <a href="/practice-areas/business-formation/">business formation and counsel</a>, and <a href="/practice-areas/elder-law/">elder law and Medicaid planning</a>. Our attorneys are licensed to practice in the Pennsylvania state courts and the U.S. District Court for the Western District of Pennsylvania.</p>
                <p>Our partners are licensed Pennsylvania title insurance agents through Chicago Title and First American, enabling us to conduct real estate closings, issue title insurance, and provide comprehensive legal counsel throughout every transaction.</p>

                <h2>Credentials & Professional Affiliations</h2>
                <p>Our attorneys hold degrees from Duquesne University School of Law, Indiana University of Pennsylvania, and Washington & Jefferson College, with credentials including J.D., M.B.A., and Summa Cum Laude honors. Our professional memberships reflect our commitment to staying at the forefront of our practice areas:</p>
