                    <li>Pennsylvania Bar Association</li>
                    <li>The Ned J. Nakles Inns of Court</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Serving Western Pennsylvania</h2>
                <p>From our office at 3950 Wm Penn Highway in Murrysville, we serve clients across <a href="/areas-we-serve/">Westmoreland, Allegheny, Washington, Butler, Fayette, and Indiana Counties</a>. Our location on Route 22 provides easy access for clients throughout the region, and we offer flexible scheduling including evening appointments.</p>
                <p>Whether you're planning for the future, navigating a property transaction, or building a business, our team is here to support your goals with dedicated, experienced counsel.</p>
